span></strong>\n\nThanks to Jitai &amp; Long-Hua Jhou (周治太, 駱龍華) picked up the bakery from QQ last week. We had an excellent bake sale and every thing was sold out within 15 mins. For those who came to parents lounge and didn\'t get any, we will have more next time.\n\nBake Sale: 3<sup>rd</sup> week on each month\n\nJesse Wei\nPrincipal, Michigan Chinese School','MCS Newsletter -10/23/2010',0,'','inherit','open','open','','100-revision','','','2010-10-22 22:19:01','2010-10-23 02:19:01','',100,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=101',0,'revision','',0),(102,1,'2010-09-22 22:24:52','2010-09-23 02:24:52','<div><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;\"> </span></span>Happy Moon Festival !. First of all, I would like to thank 韓媽媽 baked the moon cake to our students and also provided the free moon cake for all teachers.</div>\r\n<div>(1)Fall Parents meeting 1:30 pm this Saturday at parents lounge. Please be there and we need your input.</div>\r\n<div>(2)<strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><em>Home coming dress, shoes and accessory sale continue on this Saturday</em></span></strong></div>\r\n<div>(3)Free adult <strong>Mandarin Phonetic Symbols (注音符號) </strong>class enrollment at parents lounge. Class starts on 10/2</div>\r\n<div>(4)Food service on Saturday 9/25: QQ 麵包, 雞腿便當, 肉圓 ,炒米粉 ,竽頭酥, 滷雞腿 ....等. Quantity is limited.</div>\r\nJesse Wei\r\nPrincipal, Michigan Chinese School\r\n<div><a href=\"http://www.michiganchineseschool.org/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.michiganchineseschool.org/</a></div>','NCS Newsletter - 9/25/2010',0,'','inherit','open','open','','92-revision-2','','','2010-09-22 22:24:52','2010-09-23 02:24:52','',92,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=102',0,'revision','',0),(103,1,'2010-10-28 12:19:21','2010-10-28 16:19:21','<div><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: small;\"> </sp